      other graphical images, trademarks, or trademark legends.

   b) No Further Restrictions

      You may not impose further restrictions on the exercise of
      permissions granted under this License. This condition is not
      excused merely because such restrictions result from Your compliance
      with mandates or obligations extrinsic to this License (such as a
      court order or an agreement with a third party).

      Distribution of Covered Code incorporating material governed by a
      license listed in Appendix A does not impose further restrictions.
      You have permission to ignore subsection 2c solely to the extent
      necessary to comply with such other license. The requirement in
      subsection 2d to provide Corresponding Source is in no case limited
